N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 652.1 - Toll rates subject to change

State Regulations

All toll rates for the bridges are prescribed by resolution
of the commission and are subject to change without notice. The current rates
are posted and on file at the toll collectors' booths where copies are
available upon request. The latest published schedule of rates supersedes all
previous issues. Notes
